de: Amendment No 2 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs and the Republic of Slovenia represented by the Government Office for Local Self-Government and Regional Policy - 17-07-2014 - Projektabkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Slowenien, vertreten durch die Regierungsstelle für lokale Gouvernanz und Regionale Politik, betreffend die Finanzierung des Projektes «Erneuerbare Energien in den Slowenischen Alpen»
en: Amendment No 2 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs and the Republic of Slovenia represented by the Government Office for Local Self-Government and Regional Policy - 17-07-2014 - Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs and the Republic of Slovenia represented by the Government Office for local self-Government and regional policy as the National Coordination Unit concerning the Grant for the Project "Renewable Energy across the Alpine Land"
fr: Amendment No 2 to the Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs and the Republic of Slovenia represented by the Government Office for Local Self-Government and Regional Policy - 17-07-2014 - Accord de projet entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et la Slovénie, représentée par le Agence gouvernementale de l'autogouvernance locale et de la politique régionale, concernant le financement du projet «Energies renouvelables dans les Alpes slovènes»
